167
00:16:09,217 --> 00:16:10,038
[SPEAKER_01]: That has to go.

168
00:16:10,058 --> 00:16:11,560
[SPEAKER_01]: Got it.

169
00:16:13,384 --> 00:16:15,645
[SPEAKER_01]: Also the same thing with the shed in the backyard.

170
00:16:16,506 --> 00:16:18,468
[SPEAKER_01]: You refer to it as a carriage house.

171
00:16:18,508 --> 00:16:19,949
[SPEAKER_01]: We used to call it the barn.

172
00:16:20,349 --> 00:16:22,871
[SPEAKER_01]: The barn, yeah.

173
00:16:24,672 --> 00:16:31,517
[SPEAKER_01]: It's only standing because it's in tough shape.

174
00:16:31,597 --> 00:16:32,257
[SPEAKER_13]: I believe you.

175
00:16:32,738 --> 00:16:36,721
[SPEAKER_01]: My husband passed away in 2016 and I haven't been in there since.

176
00:16:38,281 --> 00:16:39,983
[SPEAKER_01]: I don't even want to go in there.

177
00:16:40,003 --> 00:16:44,848
[SPEAKER_01]: So that's really something, there's no way I can save that.

178
00:16:47,310 --> 00:16:57,401
[SPEAKER_13]: Okay, well commissioners, let's circle back to the motion on the table just so we can complete this and then depending on how the vote goes, we'll determine what the next steps are.

179
00:17:01,245 --> 00:17:06,247
[SPEAKER_13]: So just so everybody's clear, a motion was made to find for significance.

